strategy, product strategies,

00:06:04.500 --> 00:06:05.920
price strategies, promotion and

00:06:05.980 --> 00:06:07.100
distribution strategies,

00:06:07.100 --> 00:06:09.600
which are responsible, in fact,

00:06:09.620 --> 00:06:11.180
for the complex of marketing,

00:06:11.180 --> 00:06:14.940
but in this lecture we will stop

00:06:14.940 --> 00:06:16.800
on considering business strategies,

