00:06:25.880 --> 00:06:27.440
best use the resources of the enterprise

00:06:27.440 --> 00:06:29.920
to meet the needs and needs

00:06:29.920 --> 00:06:31.360
of the market.

00:06:31.560 --> 00:06:33.600
In literature, these strategies

00:06:33.600 --> 00:06:35.620
are often called basic

00:06:35.620 --> 00:06:38.180
or basic strategies.

00:06:38.520 --> 00:06:39.640
So, I would like to remind you

00:06:39.640 --> 00:06:41.520
once again that business strategies can

00:06:41.520 --> 00:06:43.620
be presented in the form of

00:06:43.620 --> 00:06:45.020
