00:06:55.660 --> 00:06:56.960
Let's start with portfolio strategies.

00:06:57.200 --> 00:06:58.980
Portfolio strategies are strategies

00:06:58.980 --> 00:07:00.680
that allow you to effectively

00:07:00.680 --> 00:07:01.920
solve the questions with which

00:07:01.920 --> 00:07:04.120
goods or services or their complexes

00:07:04.120 --> 00:07:06.340
the company will enter the

00:07:06.340 --> 00:07:07.740
market and there is a capital

00:07:07.740 --> 00:07:09.380
investment in each of

00:07:09.380 --> 00:07:10.180
the areas.

00:07:10.520 --> 00:07:12.380
That is why they are called portfolios.

00:07:12.600 --> 00:07:14.580
The fact is that companies usually do not

00:07:14.580 --> 00:07:15.820
produce one product.

00:07:15.960 --> 00:07:17.240
They produce several goods

00:07:17.240 --> 00:07:20.640
or several goods and services.

00:07:21.480 --> 00:07:24.060
And we must say that, in fact, this

00:07:24.060 --> 00:07:26.260
is the combination of all the goods and

00:07:26.260 --> 00:07:29.580
services of the company and

00:07:29.580 --> 00:07:30.500
is called a portfolio.

00:07:30.840 --> 00:07:32.700
These strategies are

00:07:32.700 --> 00:07:34.120
called portfolio

00:07:34.120 --> 00:07:35.320
strategies.

00:07:35.420 --> 00:07:37.520
The next type of strategy is

00:07:37.520 --> 00:07:38.640
a growth strategy.

00:07:38.820 --> 00:07:41.440
Growth strategies allow us to answer questions

00:07:41.440 --> 00:07:43.340
about the direction in which the enterprise

00:07:43.340 --> 00:07:44.300
should develop in order to

00:07:44.300 --> 00:07:45.840
better meet the requirements

00:07:45.840 --> 00:07:47.280
of the market, as well as questions

00:07:47.500 --> 00:07:50.140
about how to develop the entire

00:07:50.140 --> 00:07:51.540
portfolio of the enterprise

00:07:51.540 --> 00:07:54.140
and also how to develop any unit

00:07:54.140 --> 00:07:55.740
of the portfolio.

00:07:55.840 --> 00:07:58.340
Competitive strategies are

00:07:58.340 --> 00:08:00.240
strategies that help an enterprise

00:08:00.240 --> 00:08:02.600
to identify competitive

00:08:02.600 --> 00:08:04.280
advantages.

