Naturally, it is clear

00:08:06.220 --> 00:08:07.420
that competition is now

00:08:07.420 --> 00:08:09.180
increasing and companies

00:08:09.180 --> 00:08:10.860
must be able to develop

00:08:10.860 --> 00:08:12.260
strategies to compete

00:08:12.820 --> 00:08:14.840
in the market.

00:08:15.020 --> 00:08:17.100
Competitive strategies are designed

00:08:17.100 --> 00:08:18.980
to address these problems.

