01:13:04.340 --> 01:13:07.720
that companies go into completely different

01:13:07.720 --> 01:13:10.660
areas not related to the existing

01:13:10.660 --> 01:13:14.740
business, and we can distinguish

01:13:14.740 --> 01:13:19.500
two types of acquisitions

01:13:19.500 --> 01:13:21.960
in general - divergence and

01:13:21.960 --> 01:13:23.340
convergence acquisitions.

01:13:23.400 --> 01:13:24.720
We will talk about them.

01:13:25.080 --> 01:13:26.800
Divergent acquisitions or

01:13:26.800 --> 01:13:28.660
net diversification, as Lamben

01:13:28.660 --> 01:13:30.880
says, are aimed at entering

01:13:30.880 --> 01:13:32.460
a new area of market activity

01:13:32.460 --> 01:13:33.660
for the enterprise that

01:13:33.660 --> 01:13:35.600
is not related to its

01:13:35.600 --> 01:13:36.700
actual activity.

01:13:37.080 --> 01:13:38.980
But the goal is usually, of

01:13:38.980 --> 01:13:40.680
course, to expand the portfolio,

01:13:40.940 --> 01:13:44.400
to join some new completely

01:13:44.400 --> 01:13:45.900
strategic, or simply

01:13:45.980 --> 01:13:47.420
to update it.

01:13:49.100 --> 01:13:51.960
Well, the goal is to expand the presence in

01:13:51.960 --> 01:13:54.060
the market or markets and, of course,

01:13:54.520 --> 01:13:56.640
to expand the impact.

01:13:57.340 --> 01:13:59.460
Well, we must say that there

01:13:59.460 --> 01:14:01.900
are not so many examples of

01:14:01.900 --> 01:14:04.360
net diversification, because not

01:14:04.360 --> 01:14:05.900
all companies decide on net diversification,

01:14:06.000 --> 01:14:07.000
because it is really

01:14:07.000 --> 01:14:07.900
a large risk.

01:14:07.940 --> 01:14:09.640
The company needs to have

01:14:09.640 --> 01:14:11.240
a very large potential to

01:14:11.820 --> 01:14:13.660
decide on net diversification.

01:14:14.800 --> 01:14:16.440
Even Yamaha is not engaged

01:14:16.440 --> 01:14:17.940
in pure diversification, because

01:14:18.100 --> 01:14:21.420
it still works in the same

01:14:21.420 --> 01:14:22.120
area.

01:14:22.520 --> 01:14:25.120
If we talk about guitars and

01:14:25.120 --> 01:14:27.140
piano, they are musical instruments.

01:14:27.140 --> 01:14:29.040
If we talk about motorcycles,

01:14:29.040 --> 01:14:30.420
they are still

01:14:30.420 --> 01:14:32.720
consumer goods.

01:14:33.300 --> 01:14:35.480
But here is an example of pure diversification

01:14:35.480 --> 01:14:37.220
– the industrial Sergey Pugachev

01:14:37.220 --> 01:14:38.700
acquired the French chain of elite

01:14:38.700 --> 01:14:41.420
stores, restaurants Head Yard.

01:14:41.420 --> 01:14:43.760
But, nevertheless, Pogachev

01:14:43.760 --> 01:14:45.800
is already the owner of OPC, which

01:14:46.460 --> 01:14:48.580
is one of the leading companies

01:14:48.580 --> 01:14:50.420
in the field of investment management.

01:14:50.440 --> 01:14:52.180
That is, we see that there has

01:14:52.180 --> 01:14:55.660
been a pure digitization here, and

01:14:55.660 --> 01:14:58.320
Mr. Pogachev decided to simply

01:14:58.320 --> 01:15:00.360
acquire a completely different

01:15:00.360 --> 01:15:02.000
direction in order to probably

01:15:02.000 --> 01:15:04.280
strengthen his presence in other

01:15:04.280 --> 01:15:05.960
markets.

01:15:06.820 --> 01:15:07.580
But again, I want to repeat

01:15:07.580 --> 01:15:08.960
that it must be a very large

01:15:08.960 --> 01:15:11.560
company with a very large

01:15:11.560 --> 01:15:14.220
financial investment potential

01:15:14.220 --> 01:15:15.980
in order to decide

01:15:15.980 --> 01:15:17.920
on net diversification.

01:15:18.360 --> 01:15:20.280
But in addition to net diversification,

01:15:20.400 --> 01:15:23.220
apart from divergence acquisitions,

01:15:23.560 --> 01:15:24.840
there is another type of

01:15:24.840 --> 01:15:27.720
acquisition or convergence acquisition.

01:15:28.420 --> 01:15:30.780
In other words, concentric diversification.

01:15:32.160 --> 01:15:35.440
The Company goes beyond

01:15:35.440 --> 01:15:37.220
the production chain

01:15:37.220 --> 01:15:39.520
within which it has operated

01:15:39.520 --> 01:15:41.300
and seeks new activities

01:15:41.300 --> 01:15:43.400
that, nevertheless, complement

01:15:43.460 --> 01:15:45.240
an existing technological

01:15:45.240 --> 01:15:47.320
process or commercial

01:15:47.320 --> 01:15:48.620
process.

01:15:49.000 --> 01:15:50.900
In this case, the company pursues

01:15:50.900 --> 01:15:52.860
the effect of synergy.

01:15:52.900 --> 01:15:55.680
In other words, combining

01:15:55.680 --> 01:15:58.620
some processes and obtaining an

01:15:58.620 --> 01:16:00.460
enhanced process.

01:16:00.760 --> 01:16:05.440
Well, synergistic effect – An example

01:16:05.440 --> 01:16:06.340
of synergistic effect is an orchestra,

01:16:06.340 --> 01:16:08.120
when the instruments sound separately,

01:16:08.120 --> 01:16:10.220
they sound separately, when

01:16:10.220 --> 01:16:11.260
they sound in an orchestra, we

01:16:11.260 --> 01:16:12.440
hear a completely different

01:16:12.440 --> 01:16:14.540
powerful sound.

01:16:15.160 --> 01:16:18.400
For example, we must say that very much,

01:16:18.420 --> 01:16:19.560
speaking of concentric differentiation,

01:16:19.560 --> 01:16:21.280
we see many examples, especially

01:16:21.280 --> 01:16:24.440
after the reconstruction

01:16:24.440 --> 01:16:26.440
period, when Russian enterprises

01:16:26.440 --> 01:16:29.720
are forced to survive somehow,

01:16:29.720 --> 01:16:32.520
to set up the production of some

01:16:32.520 --> 01:16:35.860
goods or some products that

01:16:35.860 --> 01:16:37.180
were not directly related to

01:16:37.180 --> 01:16:40.240
the release of its traditional

01:16:40.240 --> 01:16:41.080
products.

01:16:41.120 --> 01:16:43.500
But it was somehow connected

01:16:43.500 --> 01:16:45.540
to the production chain.

01:16:45.600 --> 01:16:47.440
Well, for example, the Kirov factory

01:16:47.440 --> 01:16:48.620
in St. Petersburg, a famous factory

01:16:48.820 --> 01:16:50.440
that produced tractors.

01:16:50.500 --> 01:16:53.560
Kirovets, he in the 90s set up the

01:16:53.560 --> 01:16:54.780
production of urban buses.

01:16:54.920 --> 01:16:56.740
Many city buses are now produced

01:16:56.740 --> 01:16:58.740
at this plant.

01:16:58.740 --> 01:17:01.980
As you can see, of course, the

01:17:01.980 --> 01:17:07.140
tractor and the bus are not related

01:17:07.140 --> 01:17:08.900
mechanisms, but, nevertheless, it

01:17:08.900 --> 01:17:10.120
went beyond the production chain,

01:17:10.120 --> 01:17:12.460
but it still started to produce

01:17:12.460 --> 01:17:14.220
products that are somehow

01:17:14.220 --> 01:17:16.520
still related to the main

01:17:16.520 --> 01:17:18.500
type of its activity.

01:17:18.600 --> 01:17:22.620
As we have said, one of the opportunities

01:17:22.620 --> 01:17:28.020
of the enterprise is precisely

01:17:28.020 --> 01:17:30.600
diversification, but

01:17:30.600 --> 01:17:32.740
there are two other types.

01:17:33.180 --> 01:17:34.700
One of them is integrated

01:17:34.700 --> 01:17:35.780
development.

01:17:35.780 --> 01:17:38.100
In other words, joining a company,

01:17:38.100 --> 01:17:39.920
enterprises in order to simplify

01:17:40.520 --> 01:17:43.280
their position in the market.

01:17:43.720 --> 01:17:45.660
Integration makes sense when an

01:17:45.660 --> 01:17:47.660
enterprise intends to increase its

01:17:47.660 --> 01:17:50.660
profitability and control various

01:17:50.660 --> 01:17:52.100
strategic business units

01:17:52.100 --> 01:17:55.460
or links in the product production

01:17:55.460 --> 01:17:56.960
and sales chain.

01:17:56.960 --> 01:17:57.500


01:17:57.500 --> 01:18:00.520
Integration also exists

01:18:00.520 --> 01:18:02.140
in various forms.

01:18:02.240 --> 01:18:03.540
First of all, it is integration

01:18:03.540 --> 01:18:06.680
forward, integration backwards,

01:18:06.680 --> 01:18:07.840
and vertical integration, and

01:18:07.840 --> 01:18:09.440
horizontal integration.

01:18:09.520 --> 01:18:14.200
We will now look at these types and by type

01:18:14.200 --> 01:18:15.080
of integration.

01:18:16.540 --> 01:18:18.540
Vertical integration backwards.

01:18:18.700 --> 01:18:19.560
What is vertical?

01:18:21.200 --> 01:18:22.440
Vertical integration means that

01:18:23.100 --> 01:18:26.440
a company joins itself, that is,

01:18:26.440 --> 01:18:28.560
it is buying a business that

01:18:28.560 --> 01:18:31.900
is either linked to a general

01:18:31.900 --> 01:18:34.400
chain, but it is either linked

01:18:34.400 --> 01:18:37.680
at a previous stage or

01:18:37.680 --> 01:18:39.220
at a subsequent stage.

01:18:39.240 --> 01:18:40.180
So, if we talk about vertical

01:18:40.180 --> 01:18:42.900
integration backwards, this company

01:18:42.900 --> 01:18:44.280
takes over the management

01:18:44.280 --> 01:18:46.460
of the enterprise of the

01:18:46.460 --> 01:18:48.060
previous stage of the

01:18:48.060 --> 01:18:49.400
production chain to ensure

01:18:49.400 --> 01:18:50.840
the guaranteed quality

01:18:50.840 --> 01:18:53.860
and quantity of products delivered.

01:18:54.160 --> 01:18:56.940
Vertical back integration

01:18:56.940 --> 01:18:59.520
can be described by another

01:18:59.520 --> 01:19:04.700
marketing process, namely

01:19:04.700 --> 01:19:06.200
by building vertical

01:19:06.200 --> 01:19:07.580
marketing systems

01:19:07.580 --> 01:19:09.900
or distribution channels,

01:19:09.900 --> 01:19:12.400
where a company integrates

01:19:12.400 --> 01:19:14.040
with other companies

01:19:14.040 --> 01:19:15.580
to carry out marketing

01:19:15.580 --> 01:19:16.860
activities, from

01:19:17.200 --> 01:19:18.380
production to product

01:19:18.420 --> 01:19:20.160
distribution.

01:19:20.460 --> 01:19:23.940
In this case, if we are talking about

01:19:23.940 --> 01:19:27.420
vertical integration back, then

01:19:27.420 --> 01:19:30.860
the company buys some companies

01:19:30.860 --> 01:19:32.880
that are suppliers

01:19:32.880 --> 01:19:34.100
to the company.

01:19:34.840 --> 01:19:35.200
For what?

01:19:35.320 --> 01:19:37.300
To control the entire

01:19:37.300 --> 01:19:40.220
process, to protect the

01:19:44.480 --> 01:19:47.440
market from competitors.

01:19:47.840 --> 01:19:50.260
A good example here will be the

01:19:50.260 --> 01:19:51.500
Zoo Baltimore Holding.

01:19:51.740 --> 01:19:54.180
As you know, the company Baltimore

01:19:54.180 --> 01:19:59.460
produces food products.

01:20:00.080 --> 01:20:02.880
These are ketchups, these are sauces,

01:20:02.880 --> 01:20:04.900
this is mayonnaise, these are processed

01:20:04.900 --> 01:20:07.080
canned fruits and vegetables.

01:20:07.100 --> 01:20:08.440
What did the company do?

01:20:08.880 --> 01:20:13.300
It has not only bought the fields

01:20:13.300 --> 01:20:15.380
on which these tomatoes grow, that

01:20:15.380 --> 01:20:17.240
is, it already owns farms, but also

01:20:17.240 --> 01:20:19.620
bought the companies that were

01:20:19.620 --> 01:20:21.960
engaged in the production

01:20:21.960 --> 01:20:23.720
of the tar.

01:20:24.260 --> 01:20:26.140
The company also bought

01:20:26.140 --> 01:20:27.960
transport companies that are

01:20:27.960 --> 01:20:31.680
engaged in the transportation

01:20:31.680 --> 01:20:33.960
of this agricultural products

01:20:33.960 --> 01:20:35.720
to factories that process

01:20:35.720 --> 01:20:36.580
this product.

01:20:36.580 --> 01:20:41.900
In other words, the company has done

01:20:41.900 --> 01:20:45.220
the integration procedure back,

01:20:45.220 --> 01:20:47.440
and now we see that the whole process,

01:20:47.680 --> 01:20:50.180
the technological process, is

01:20:50.180 --> 01:20:52.960
built into one chain and is

01:20:52.960 --> 01:20:55.360
under the control of the Baltimore

01:20:55.360 --> 01:20:56.320
Holding Hall, that is, the

01:20:56.320 --> 01:20:57.960
company organized Holding.

01:20:58.340 --> 01:21:00.220
Vertical integration forward is

01:21:00.440 --> 01:21:02.400
actually integration with the enterprises

01:21:02.400 --> 01:21:04.400
of the subsequent stage of production

01:21:04.400 --> 01:21:07.420
in order to also guarantee

01:21:07.420 --> 01:21:08.980
product sales and

01:21:08.980 --> 01:21:10.900
better distribution.

01:21:12.840 --> 01:21:14.660
We can say that there are many

01:21:14.660 --> 01:21:17.040
examples of integration in general.

01:21:17.200 --> 01:21:18.680
For example, it is Rosneft, which

01:21:18.680 --> 01:21:22.420
not only mines oil, processes

01:21:22.720 --> 01:21:23.960
oil, stores oil, but also

01:21:23.960 --> 01:21:27.280
has its columns in various

01:21:27.280 --> 01:21:29.520
countries.

01:21:30.440 --> 01:21:32.440
This is also companies that

01:21:32.440 --> 01:21:36.480
are engaged in the processing

01:21:36.480 --> 01:21:37.740
and production of fuel, it is Lukoel,

01:21:38.320 --> 01:21:39.820
for example, Lukoel, as Rosneft

01:21:39.820 --> 01:21:42.540
has a very large network of business

01:21:42.540 --> 01:21:44.200
locks not only in Russia, but also

01:21:44.200 --> 01:21:46.500
in Europe, Lithuania, Hungary,

01:21:46.500 --> 01:21:48.260
Poland and even the United

01:21:48.260 --> 01:21:49.040
States.

01:21:49.320 --> 01:21:53.100
In other words, by joining,

01:21:53.120 --> 01:21:57.520
integrating into its system these

01:21:57.520 --> 01:21:59.000
companies that are engaged

01:21:59.000 --> 01:22:01.080
in the delivery of fuel consumers,

01:22:01.120 --> 01:22:02.600
the company controls and best

01:22:02.600 --> 01:22:04.780
brings products to consumers.

01:22:05.460 --> 01:22:07.320
I have already said that

01:22:07.320 --> 01:22:08.100
building a vertical marketing

01:22:08.100 --> 01:22:10.820
system is the same process,

01:22:10.820 --> 01:22:13.980
but from a different perspective.

01:22:13.980 --> 01:22:14.920


01:22:15.180 --> 01:22:16.580
Therefore, it must be said

01:22:16.580 --> 01:22:17.560
that the construction of

01:22:17.560 --> 01:22:19.880
franchise companies, which

01:22:19.880 --> 01:22:20.880
are vertical marketing systems,

01:22:20.880 --> 01:22:23.360
is integration forward.

01:22:23.360 --> 01:22:25.380
The company "Evroshe" is known to everyone,

01:22:25.400 --> 01:22:26.560
especially ladies.

01:22:26.800 --> 01:22:28.220
A company that researches,

01:22:28.220 --> 01:22:31.940
produces products, perfume products,

01:22:31.940 --> 01:22:37.500
it also brings it to consumers

01:22:37.500 --> 01:22:41.940
through its points.

01:22:42.160 --> 01:22:43.840
In other words, it opens stores

01:22:43.840 --> 01:22:45.240
in all countries, it is

01:22:45.240 --> 01:22:46.680
a franchise company, and under

01:22:46.680 --> 01:22:48.840
the auspices of “Evroshe”,

01:22:48.840 --> 01:22:52.400
they sell products of “Evroshe”.

01:22:52.460 --> 01:22:55.380
I have to say that companies often

01:22:55.380 --> 01:22:57.600
combine two integration processes

01:22:57.600 --> 01:22:58.440
– forward and back.

01:22:58.560 --> 01:23:01.700
And many companies, especially

01:23:01.700 --> 01:23:03.160
companies that are engaged

01:23:03.160 --> 01:23:04.760
in oil refining, they integrate

01:23:05.420 --> 01:23:07.140
both forward and backwards

01:23:07.140 --> 01:23:08.480
at the same time.

01:23:08.740 --> 01:23:11.100
And now we have considered with you

01:23:11.100 --> 01:23:13.420
the vertical integration forward and back.

01:23:13.700 --> 01:23:15.080
Let us go to horizontal integration.

01:23:15.320 --> 01:23:16.660
This is another type of integration.

01:23:17.000 --> 01:23:19.660
Horizon integration and strategy

01:23:19.660 --> 01:23:22.640
have a completely different perspective.

01:23:22.720 --> 01:23:23.280
What is the goal?

01:23:23.360 --> 01:23:25.120
This will strengthen the company's position

01:23:25.120 --> 01:23:27.120
by acquiring and controlling

01:23:27.120 --> 01:23:29.320
other companies competing companies

01:23:29.320 --> 01:23:32.160
to increase market share, to

01:23:32.160 --> 01:23:35.360
increase, to ensure leadership,

01:23:35.360 --> 01:23:36.920
well, and, of course, to

01:23:36.920 --> 01:23:38.260
make more profits.

01:23:38.420 --> 01:23:41.040
Well, to implement horizontal integration,

01:23:41.040 --> 01:23:43.040
the company sets the task of

01:23:43.040 --> 01:23:45.820
neutralizing existing competitors.

01:23:46.000 --> 01:23:49.220
We see many examples of companies

01:23:49.220 --> 01:23:53.940
merging, and sometimes this

01:23:53.940 --> 01:23:56.460
merger happens on a mutual arrangement,

01:23:56.460 --> 01:23:57.480
like Pricewaterhouse, CoopersLibrant,

01:23:57.480 --> 01:23:59.180
two large companies merged,

01:23:59.720 --> 01:24:01.220
it's also a horizontal

01:24:01.220 --> 01:24:02.640
integration.

01:24:02.920 --> 01:24:06.140
Well, or here is an example, very

01:24:06.140 --> 01:24:08.240
classic, is the merger of two

01:24:08.240 --> 01:24:09.620
automotive giants Daimler-

01:24:09.620 --> 01:24:13.240
Benz and Chrysler.

01:24:14.760 --> 01:24:16.860
Many examples can be given.

01:24:16.860 --> 01:24:21.060
I can give you an example because of,

01:24:21.060 --> 01:24:23.380
for example, two companies in Lithuania,

01:24:24.740 --> 01:24:28.360
two supermarket chains, Maxim and Sauliutya.

01:24:28.580 --> 01:24:31.700
Sauliutya was smaller to the network,

01:24:31.700 --> 01:24:33.680
it was absorbed by the company

01:24:33.680 --> 01:24:36.920
Maxim, and now in Lithuania

01:24:36.920 --> 01:24:40.220
there is one network, this is

01:24:40.440 --> 01:24:41.820
Maxim, which is represented by

01:24:41.820 --> 01:24:43.500
various types of stores.

01:24:43.600 --> 01:24:45.200
But, nevertheless, the

01:24:45.200 --> 01:24:47.580
company has absorbed another

01:24:47.580 --> 01:24:49.060
company, a smaller competitor,

01:24:49.180 --> 01:24:50.800
to expand its presence.

01:24:50.980 --> 01:24:51.960
Of course it is integration.

01:24:52.040 --> 01:24:53.720
There are many such examples,

01:24:53.720 --> 01:24:55.700
and, in fact, if we look at

01:24:55.700 --> 01:24:59.640
what percentage of types of integration,

01:24:59.640 --> 01:25:00.700
horizontal integration will

01:25:00.700 --> 01:25:03.020
probably take more than 50

01:25:03.020 --> 01:25:05.340
or 60 percent, because it is the

01:25:05.340 --> 01:25:07.820
logically determined business

01:25:07.820 --> 01:25:09.840
process, it is the absorption

01:25:09.840 --> 01:25:11.420
of a weaker competitor

01:25:11.420 --> 01:25:13.060
to simplify their positions

01:25:13.060 --> 01:25:15.700
and to take a larger

01:25:15.700 --> 01:25:17.620
market share.

01:25:17.880 --> 01:25:20.160
All of these strategies are outputted

01:25:20.160 --> 01:25:21.820
into, can be represented in the

01:25:21.820 --> 01:25:23.080
outer acquisition matrix.

01:25:23.360 --> 01:25:25.520
So we see two different processes here

01:25:25.520 --> 01:25:27.380
– diversification and integration.

01:25:28.180 --> 01:25:30.640
We see new areas and old areas.

01:25:30.740 --> 01:25:32.660
So we see two processes in diversification

01:25:32.660 --> 01:25:35.460
– the implicit acquisitions

01:25:35.460 --> 01:25:37.100
and the convergent acquisitions,

01:25:37.100 --> 01:25:38.360
which we just talked about,

01:25:38.360 --> 01:25:41.080
and we see integrations.

01:25:41.160 --> 01:25:42.500
There are two types of integration: vertical

01:25:42.500 --> 01:25:44.040
